title: Match history page not loading?
body: I've tried to access the Match history page to look at my friend's match history, but it seems like I cannot access it in any way. It just does not load for me. Are any one of you people having the same problem?

replies.body: Same for me, it doesn't load on any browser even though I've cleared data on all of them
Does this still happen if you use a different browser or if you [clear your browser's data](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) beforehand?
